        <updateDate>2004-06-23T18:52:49Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Prohibits Federal agencies from awarding grants, contracts, loan guarantees, and other funding to companies of interest (as defined under this Act) that have outsourced jobs during the previous five years, except as specified under this Act or for national security purposes.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
